### ============================================================
### Quiza V2 — E2E API Test (VS Code REST Client)
### 순서대로 실행하면 전체 플로우를 테스트할 수 있습니다.
###
### 사전 준비:
###   1. VS Code 확장 "REST Client" 설치 (humao.rest-client)
###   2. npm run start:dev  (서버 실행 — localhost:8080)
###   3. 각 섹션의 "Send Request" 클릭
###
### 응답에서 받은 ID를 다음 요청의 변수에 복사해서 사용하세요.
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ----- 0. Health Check -----

GET {{baseUrl}}/health HTTP/1.1

### ----- 1. Auth: Dev Login (쿠키 발급) -----

# @name devLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/dev-login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "world_id": "test-user-001"
}

### ----- 2. Auth: Get Nonce -----

GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/nonce HTTP/1.1

### ----- 3. Auth: Me (로그인 확인) -----
### devLogin 응답의 Set-Cookie에서 access_token 값을 복사하세요.

@token = {{devLogin.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

# @name me
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me HTTP/1.1
Cookie: {{token}}

### ----- 4. Domains: 목록 조회 -----

# @name domains
GET {{baseUrl}}/domains HTTP/1.1
Cookie: {{token}}

### ----- 5. Goals: 학습 목표 생성 -----
### domains 응답에서 id를 복사하여 domain_id에 넣으세요.

@domainId = PASTE_DOMAIN_ID_HERE

# @name createGoal
POST {{baseUrl}}/goals HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{token}}

{
  "domain_id": "{{domainId}}",
  "target": "TOEIC 800",
  "level": "intermediate"
}

### ----- 6. Roadmaps: 로드맵 생성 -----
### createGoal 응답에서 id를 복사하여 goalId에 넣으세요.

@goalId = PASTE_GOAL_ID_HERE

# @name createRoadmap
POST {{baseUrl}}/roadmaps HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{token}}

{
  "goal_id": "{{goalId}}"
}

### ----- 7. Roadmaps: 로드맵 조회 -----
### createRoadmap 응답에서 id를 복사하여 roadmapId에 넣으세요.

@roadmapId = PASTE_ROADMAP_ID_HERE

GET {{baseUrl}}/roadmaps/{{roadmapId}} HTTP/1.1
Cookie: {{token}}

### ----- 8. Roadmaps: 진행률 조회 -----

GET {{baseUrl}}/roadmaps/{{roadmapId}}/progress HTTP/1.1
Cookie: {{token}}

### ----- 9. Sessions: 학습 세션 생성 -----
### 로드맵 조회 응답의 checkpoints[0].id를 복사하여 checkpointId에 넣으세요.

@checkpointId = PASTE_CHECKPOINT_ID_HERE

# @name createSession
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{token}}

{
  "checkpoint_id": "{{checkpointId}}"
}

### ----- 10. Answers: 답안 제출 -----
### createSession 응답의 questions[0].id를 복사하여 questionId에 넣으세요.

@questionId = PASTE_QUESTION_ID_HERE

# @name submitAnswer
POST {{baseUrl}}/answers HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{token}}

{
  "question_id": "{{questionId}}",
  "user_answer": "A"
}

### ----- 11. Stats: 학습 통계 조회 -----

GET {{baseUrl}}/stats HTTP/1.1
Cookie: {{token}}

### ----- 12. Questions: AI 문제 생성 (프리미엄 전용) -----
### is_premium=false 유저는 403 응답을 받습니다.

POST {{baseUrl}}/questions/generate HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{token}}

{
  "tag": "grammar",
  "difficulty": 3,
  "count": 5
}

### ----- 13. Auth: Logout -----

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout HTTP/1.1
Cookie: {{token}}

### ----- 14. Auth: Me (로그아웃 확인 — 401 예상) -----

GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me HTTP/1.1
